step.tex:
\begin{align}
\frac{dy}{dx} &\geq 0, x\in [a,b] \implies\text{ increasing in } [a,b] \\
\frac{dy}{dx} &\leq 0, x\in [a,b] \implies\text{ decreasing in } [a,b] \\
\end{align}

%text
(i) the function is increasing - but \underline\text{not strictly} 
(ii) the function is decreasing - but \underline\text{not strictly} 
%
